The very last time 2pac entered a rating into the ratebeer database he said of Miller Genuine Draft  "i dont mind this beer. Its very easy drinking, and goes down well when you’re really thirsty." Expressing satisfaction in both the flavor, palate, and thirst quenching abilities of this beer. &lt;bra /&gt;
I once had this on Draught on a floating casino in Dubuque Iowa, right before I won about $40 in a slot machine. So it’s a lucky beer. &lt;bra /&gt;


This beer pours a particularly pale golden color with medium tight white head. &lt;bra /&gt;


The aroma is a lot of corn and alcohol with a mild toasty maltiness. &lt;bra /&gt;


The beer tastes almost exactly like it smells, some corn, some toasty malt, a little alcohol. Perhaps there is a bit more fruitiness in the flavor than the aroma but I think 2pac nailed it here. This stuff would be great if I was really thirsty.

Cerveja de baixa fermentação, Pilsen, fabricada no Brasil, long neck. Ótima cerveja para dias quentes, leve amargor, refrescante, sem gosto predominante, suave. Preço médio acima das cervejas populares. Muito vendida em bares noturnos. Na falta de uma nova para experimentar é ela a escolhida.
/////.
Lager beer, pilsen, brasilian long neck. Very goog in a hot day, light bitter, refresh, but do not have a predominant taste.
